  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153273_103_569-679",
      "chapterUid": 103,
      "range": "569-679",
      "markText": "现在已然衰朽者，将来可能重放异彩。 现在备受青睐者，将来却可能黯然失色。 贺拉斯《诗艺》",
      "totalCount": 275,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153273&chapterUid=103&rangeStart=569&rangeEnd=679",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/89c32460813aba25fg01310e?chapterUid=103&rangeStart=569&rangeEnd=679"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153273_24_5186-5249",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "5186-5249",
      "markText": "长期以来的经验显示，大部分投资者在以过高价格购买绩优企业的证券方面的损失，比为获得较高收益或利润购买不良企业的证券的损失更少。",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153273&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=5186&rangeEnd=5249",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/89c32460813aba25fg01310e?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=5186&rangeEnd=5249"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153273_24_11504-11584",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "11504-11584",
      "markText": "稳定是一个真正的定性因素，因为它首先源自业务性质，而非统计记录。虽然企业稳定的统计记录可以表明该业务本质上是稳定的，但这个统计记录得出的结论可能被其他因素颠覆。",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153273&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=11504&rangeEnd=11584",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/89c32460813aba25fg01310e?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=11504&rangeEnd=11584"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153273_23_5363-5433",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "5363-5433",
      "markText": "最重要的一点是，证券分析并不是为了确定某只证券的内在价值，而是为了证明其内在价值是足够的，例如能够为债券提供保障或者能够为购买股票提供依据。",
      "totalCount": 169,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153273&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=5363&rangeEnd=5433",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/89c32460813aba25fg01310e?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=5363&rangeEnd=5433"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153273_23_5491-5563",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "5491-5563",
      "markText": "打个简单的比方，我们很有可能只需通过观察，就能判断一个女人是否达到了投票的年纪，而无须知其岁数；或者判断一个男人的体重是否超标，而无须知其体重。",
      "totalCount": 150,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153273&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=5491&rangeEnd=5563",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/89c32460813aba25fg01310e?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=5491&rangeEnd=5563"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153273_24_10955-11017",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "10955-11017",
      "markText": "股价经常过度涨跌的根本原因是：当价值主要由前景决定时，由此产生的判断就不受任何数学分析的控制，并且几乎不可避免地会走向极端。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153273&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=10955&rangeEnd=11017",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/89c32460813aba25fg01310e?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=10955&rangeEnd=11017"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153273_16_6470-6511",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "6470-6511",
      "markText": "投资者需要始终抵制一种倾向：对价格上涨的投资过于热情，却对价格下跌的投资进行抛售。",
      "totalCount": 140,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153273&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=6470&rangeEnd=6511",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/89c32460813aba25fg01310e?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=6470&rangeEnd=6511"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153273_8_874-966",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "874-966",
      "markText": "当时的投资人在狂热的氛围中已经不再参考确定的股息回报、稳定充足的盈利记录以及有形资产的安全保障，而全面转向对未来盈利的预测，线性外推盈利上升的趋势，逐渐将希望资本化而忘记了估值的约束。",
      "totalCount": 136,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153273&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=874&rangeEnd=966",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/89c32460813aba25fg01310e?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=874&rangeEnd=966"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153273_5_5250-5328",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "5250-5328",
      "markText": "投资不是去预测情绪或市场风向，而是回到企业本身；不是追求“看上去合理”的解释，而是分辨自己真正理解的部分；不是努力避免所有损失，而是学会在不确定中留出余地。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153273&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5250&rangeEnd=5328",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/89c32460813aba25fg01310e?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5250&rangeEnd=5328"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153273_22_942-1255",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "942-1255",
      "markText": "毕业后，数学系、哲学系和英语系的主任都向他抛出了留校任教的橄榄枝，但哥伦比亚学院的院长更倾向于将优秀学生送往华尔街。",
      "totalCount": 120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153273&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=942&rangeEnd=1255",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/89c32460813aba25fg01310e?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=942&rangeEnd=1255"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153273_6_1018-1107",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1018-1107",
      "markText": "直到读了格雷厄姆和多德的著作并聆听了他们的教诲之后，我才意识到我的“取经之旅”结束了。多年来，我一直遵循着两位恩师阐述的投资路线图。对我而言，没有任何理由再去寻找其他的投资方法。",
      "totalCount": 119,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153273&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1018&rangeEnd=1107",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/89c32460813aba25fg01310e?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1018&rangeEnd=1107"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153273_10_1447-1492",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "1447-1492",
      "markText": "现象能够反映本质，现象和本质都会变化，但是本质不如现象变化得快，核心是如何通过现象看本质。",
      "totalCount": 112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153273&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1447&rangeEnd=1492",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/89c32460813aba25fg01310e?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1447&rangeEnd=1492"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153273_22_1731-1788",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "1731-1788",
      "markText": "。尽管有他母亲的前车之鉴，格雷厄姆还是以保证金购买股票。结果，他被迫亏本卖出，并花了两年时间来弥补教授的资金损失。",
      "totalCount": 112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153273&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=1731&rangeEnd=1788",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/89c32460813aba25fg01310e?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=1731&rangeEnd=1788"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153273_13_3903-3977",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "3903-3977",
      "markText": "一个事物有很多个维度，当其中有一两个维度的变化特别锐利，锐利到足以决定成败时，那我们据此做出决策往往具有很高的成功概率，我将这类决策称为“简单决策”",
      "totalCount": 105,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153273&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=3903&rangeEnd=3977",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/89c32460813aba25fg01310e?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=3903&rangeEnd=3977"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153273_22_17094-17147",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "17094-17147",
      "markText": "加密货币几乎符合格雷厄姆所有关于投机的测试标准：它完全依赖于市场走势，缺乏明确的内在价值，并且具有高杠杆性",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153273&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=17094&rangeEnd=17147",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/89c32460813aba25fg01310e?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=17094&rangeEnd=17147"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153273_54_5648-5722",
      "chapterUid": 54,
      "range": "5648-5722",
      "markText": "对于投资者而言，要深入钻研业务，仿佛自己就是这家公司的所有者，而非仅仅停留在管理层的讨论或分析师的报告上。唯有如此，你才能真正地将各个环节串联起来。",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153273&chapterUid=54&rangeStart=5648&rangeEnd=5722",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/89c32460813aba25fg01310e?chapterUid=54&rangeStart=5648&rangeEnd=5722"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153273_23_6075-6128",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "6075-6128",
      "markText": "分析师无法就内在价值与市场价格的关系得出一个可靠的结论。即便如此，如果价格过高或过低，还是可以得出结论的。",
      "totalCount": 98,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153273&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=6075&rangeEnd=6128",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/89c32460813aba25fg01310e?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=6075&rangeEnd=6128"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153273_8_2169-2222",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2169-2222",
      "markText": "就如《证券分析》扉页引用的诗句：“现在已然衰朽者，将来可能重放异彩。现在备受青睐者，将来却可能黯然失色。”",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153273&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2169&rangeEnd=2222",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/89c32460813aba25fg01310e?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2169&rangeEnd=2222"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153273_16_7269-7315",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "7269-7315",
      "markText": "人们倾向于认为他们最近经历过的事件在未来很可能再次发生，而最近没有发生的事件很可能不再发生。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153273&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=7269&rangeEnd=7315",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/89c32460813aba25fg01310e?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=7269&rangeEnd=7315"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153273_16_10148-10197",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "10148-10197",
      "markText": "强大的壁垒、较低的资本需求、有机增长、回头客、显著的定价权、高利润率、低技术过时风险、竞争护城河。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153273&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=10148&rangeEnd=10197",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/89c32460813aba25fg01310e?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=10148&rangeEnd=10197"
    }
